        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Square Foot Calculator</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Stop guessing how much material you need. Our free square foot calculator instantly determines the exact area of your ro...</p>
